title: DAZ3D - Asian River Bundle
description:
Another resurrection

ASIAN RIVER BUNDLE
------------------

This bundle includes:


Kiaria for Mei Lin 7
-------------------- 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/63d543497265821fdb9fcf59d020ee57.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/24411

Add a little Asian flare to your Daz Studio library with this beautiful character set from 3DSublimeProductions and Sabby. Beautifully toned skin, gorgeous makeups, and stunning eyes make this new morph for Mei Lin 7, an absolutely must have for your collection!


Kai for Lee 7
------------- 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/e35e21f8c24123557d786309be61c546.jpg


www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/30751

Kai is a handsome new character for Lee 7. Kai includes Custom Sculpted HD Head and Body Morphs to give Lee 7 a unique new look. Kai includes 6 eye colors and a custom shoulder tattoo. The skin was crafted from high-res photos and the textures are based on Genesis 3 Male Base UV maps. 


Asian River
----------- 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/a28b8e7de5ff39cd196eb5a9ccbdc1b1.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/30762

Travel on the Asian shore or aboard a mythical Thailand Longtail boat.


DA Village Life Poses for Lee 7
------------------------------- 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/78eb02ea3ff1d6192f78fdbe488e672c.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/31647

A set of village life poses for Lee 7 and Genesis 3 Male(s) with environment Poses for use with the Asian River Set.This set includes:

20 Base centered poses for Genesis 3 Male(s)
20 Environment positioned poses for use with Lee 7 and the Asian River Environment
Zero Location and Zero Pose utility Poses
10 Location set Poses To position figure in the Asian River environment with no actual Pose data.
1 Boat Pose for Asian River Boat prop. For use with boat poses.

20 Environment positioned poses for use with Mei Lin 7 and the Asian River Environment
Zero Location and Zero Pose utility Poses
